These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-1::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, strawberry, orange, corn
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, board-games, skydiving, drawing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, badminton, sailing, tennis
 1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an odd position##4
 2. the person eating corn is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##8
 4. the person who's sport is parkour is not the person eating corn##6
 5. the person eating orange is somewhere to the right of the person eating blueberry##5
 6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 7. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the left of the person eating strawberry##8
 8. the person eating strawberry is not the person who's sport is tennis##6
 9. the person eating blueberry is not the person who's hobby is drawing##6
10. the person who's sport is badminton is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
11. the person eating strawberry is not to the right of the person who's sport is sailing##8
12. the person eating strawberry is in an even position##4
13. the person eating corn is not to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##8
14. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not to the right of the person who's sport is sailing##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Food    | blueberry         | corn     | orange     | strawberry         |
| Hobby   | board-games | drawing    | skydiving     | cooking |
| Sport   | parkour       | badminton | tennis | sailing       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, almond-milk, soy-milk, 7up
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, doctor, coach, firefighter
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, skiing, surfing, basketball
 1. the coach is not to the right of the firefighter##8
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is the doctor##1
 5. the journalist is not the person drinking soy-milk##6
 6. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 7. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the journalist##1
 8. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the coach##5
10. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | soy-milk          | sprite      | 7up      | almond-milk   |
| Job        | coach     | journalist | doctor | firefighter      |
| Sport      | basketball | skiing    | tennis  | surfing |

