.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, puzzles, photography, collecting
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, disco, metal, hip-hop
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, bus, jet-ski, taxi
 1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 2. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the person driving the jet-ski##5
 3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
 4. the fan of disco is somewhere to the left of the person driving the taxi##5
 5. the person driving the helicopter is not the fan of soul##6
 6. the fan of soul is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 7. the fan of soul is not to the right of the fan of hip-hop##8
 8. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the fan of metal##1
 9. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an even position##4
10. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | photography  | puzzles | collecting | drawing |
| Music-Genre   | disco  | soul      | hip-hop | metal        |
| Transport     | helicopter | jet-ski       | taxi    | bus     |

