.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, martial-arts, satire, fantasy
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, classical, country, ambient
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, dutch, french, indonesian
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
 2. the dutch is not to the left of the fan of classical##8
 3. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the right of the person watching sports movies##5
 4. the person watching sports movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching martial-arts movies is not to the right of the dutch##8
 6. the french is not to the right of the person watching fantasy movies##8
 7. the fan of country is somewhere to the left of the person watching fantasy movies##5
 8. the indonesian is somewhere to the right of the dutch##5
 9. the argentine is on the left of the french##1
10. the person watching fantasy movies is the french##1
11. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the right of the fan of classical##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | sports   | fantasy | martial-arts    | satire |
| Music-Genre   | country    | classical     | reggae   | ambient     |
| Nationality   | argentine | french   | dutch | indonesian    |

