.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, board-games, baking, magic-tricks
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, superhero, crime, disaster
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, sailing, weightlifting, biathlon
 1. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##5
 2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
 3. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##5
 5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 6. the person watching disaster movies is not the person who's hobby is baking##6
 7. the person who's hobby is camping is not the person who's sport is weightlifting##6
 8. the person watching superhero movies is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 9. the person watching crime movies is not to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##8
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person who's hobby is baking##1
11. the person who's sport is biathlon is not to the left of the person watching crime movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | baking       | camping | board-games  | magic-tricks    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime       | disaster    | superhero | horror    |
| Sport         | biathlon | water-polo   | weightlifting   | sailing |

