.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-6::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, strawberry, tomato, radish
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, satire, disaster, animation
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, german, egyptian, indonesian
 1. the person eating tomato is not to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##8
 2. the person watching animation movies is not the german##6
 3. the egyptian is somewhere between the person eating strawberry and the person watching animation movies##7
 4. the german is not to the left of the person watching satire movies##8
 5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
 6. the egyptian is the person watching time-travel movies##1
 7. the person eating cabbage is somewhere to the right of the person watching disaster movies##5
 8. the indonesian is between the person eating cabbage and the egyptian##2
 9. the person watching animation movies is not to the right of the person eating cabbage##8
10. the person eating tomato is not to the right of the person eating radish##8
11. the indian is somewhere to the left of the person watching animation movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Food          | strawberry      | tomato      | radish | cabbage |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | time-travel    | animation | satire     |
| Nationality   | indian    | egyptian | indonesian  | german |

