 3. the mexican is between the french and the person driving the bike##2
 4. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 5. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the french##3
 6. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 7. the person driving the bike is not the japanese##6
 8. the person watching thriller movies is not to the right of the japanese##8
 9. the japanese is not to the left of the person driving the bike##8
10. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5
11. the person watching thriller movies is not to the left of the japanese##8
12. the person watching zombie movies is not to the left of the person driving the motorbike##8
13. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the motorbike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |     4      |
