There 4 different types of food: banana, pumpkin, watermelon, apple
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, reggae, folk, ambient
1. the person eating watermelon is somewhere to the right of the person eating apple##5
2. the person eating banana is somewhere between the person eating apple and the person eating watermelon##7
3. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
4. the fan of folk is not to the right of the person drinking milk##8
5. the person eating apple is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
6. the person eating banana is not to the right of the person drinking cola##8
7. the person eating apple is the fan of reggae##1
8. the person eating apple is somewhere between the fan of ambient and the person drinking water##7
9. the person eating apple is on the left of the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | water     | tea | cola  | milk |
| Food          | pumpkin | apple   | banana | watermelon |
| Music-Genre   | techno     | reggae   | ambient      | folk      |

