 1. the person who's hobby is board-games is not to the right of the person driving the boat##8
 2. the british is somewhere between the person driving the motorbike and the italian##7
 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the person driving the roller##8
 4. the person driving the roller is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the thai is not to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##8
 7. the british is on the left or right of the thai##3
 8. the thai is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5
 9. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the person driving the boat##8
10. the person driving the van is not to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
11. the thai is not to the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##8
12. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
13. the thai is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##5
14. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |      3      |     4      |
