 4. the person eating artichoke is not to the left of the person eating cherry##8
 5. the person eating mango is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
 6. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5
 7. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
 9. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
