.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-13::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, fisherman, firefighter, librarian
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, spanish, indian, japanese
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, helicopter, trike, scooter
 1. the japanese is somewhere to the right of the indian##5
 2. the lawyer is on the left of the japanese##1
