 4. the person driving the van is on the left of the japanese##1
 5. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the fisherman##1
 6. the firefighter is on the right of the lawyer##1
 7. the librarian is the person driving the helicopter##1
 8. the person driving the van is not the fisherman##6
 9. the librarian is not to the left of the dutch##8
10. the dutch is not to the right of the fisherman##8
11. the firefighter is somewhere between the dutch and the person driving the van##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |    3     |    4    |
| Job           | lawyer  | firefighter | fisherman | librarian |
| Nationality   | indian | japanese           | dutch  | spanish |
| Transport     | van      | trike           | scooter     | helicopter  |

